title: Hour 2 - Westbrook vs. Westbrick, LIV Tour Isn't Serious Golf
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Westbrook vs. Westbrick, LIV Tour Isn't Serious Golf
description:
Dan weighs in on Nick Saban's latest comments and Russell Westbrook's legacy, and says he won't take the LIV Golf Tour seriously until they start playing serious golf. USA Today Columnist Dan Wolken stops by to take a first look at the college football season.
